1
00:00:10,240 --> 00:00:11,840
The contract is in the study.

2
00:00:12,520 --> 00:00:13,920
I hid it under the desk.

3
00:00:15,680 --> 00:00:16,520
Got it.

4
00:00:17,840 --> 00:00:18,800
Go back now.

5
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:07,480
My dear brother,

6
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:09,800
you really have some nerve.

7
00:01:10,039 --> 00:01:11,500
Why are you back this time?

8
00:01:12,160 --> 00:01:13,440
Don't tell me you missed me,

9
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:14,800
your big brother?

10
00:01:18,080 --> 00:01:19,240
My dear brother,

11
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:20,680
I came back...

12
00:01:21,039 --> 00:01:23,120
To avenge my mother, of course.

13
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,440
Still unrepentant?

14
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:27,960
Song Huainan,

15
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:30,130
you're the one who deserves to die.

16
00:01:31,039 --> 00:01:31,800
Seize her.

17
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,130
No need to chase.

18
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,640
Did you find her?

19
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,640
Marshal, we found her.

20
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,440
Good.

21
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:26,760
Luo Li.

22
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,120
Be gentle with my ex-wife.

23
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,160
Zhu Luoli.

24
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:04,920
Sometimes I have to admire you.

25
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:07,040
You played us all for fools.

26
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,600
You're quite something.

27
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:12,440
I really didn't expect this.

28
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:14,880
No wonder we couldn't find your body.

29
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:16,000
It's just a pity

30
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:19,360
about that memorial tablet we set up for you.

31
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,800
Since you already know,

32
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:23,120
do with me as you please.

33
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:26,520
It's just a pity

34
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:29,560
that in the end, I couldn't avenge my father

35
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,120
and kill a demon like you.

36
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:43,480
Demon?

37
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,200
No, no, no.

38
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,079
I'm no demon.

39
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,160
Zhu Luoli.

40
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,120
This dagger...

41
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:12,040
I'm not the owner of this dagger,

42
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:14,920
but you should be very familiar with its owner.

43
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,290
What do you mean?

44
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,529
Why don't you ask him yourself?

45
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,200
Luoli.

46
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,960
Here he comes.

47
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:26,960
Hurry.

48
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:29,840
Song Huainan, what do you want?

49
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:33,159
Let her go.

50
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:35,560
Don't you want to avenge your family?

51
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,600
Here is your chance.

52
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,120
Come on.

53
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:42,560
Hold it.

54
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:53,280
Do you have feelings for your sister-in-law?

55
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,040
Yes.

56
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:56,140
As long as you divorce her,

57
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:58,120
I can marry her.

58
00:05:18,080 --> 00:05:18,840
Qingzhou.

59
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:21,880
Is this yours?

60
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:28,640
Luoli.

61
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:29,920
Is this your knife?

62
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:22,480
So this is what they call

63
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,080
love.

64
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,400
Alright.

65
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:35,600
Song Qingzhou.

66
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,200
Right now,

67
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:40,680
you look just like a clown.

68
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,290
Get the hell out.

69
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,040
No need.

70
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:06,840
A stray dog

71
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,600
is nothing to fear.

72
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:33,320
Good.

73
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,159
Revenge is served.

74
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:37,000
Come, let's celebrate.

75
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:39,440
Zhu Luoli.

76
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:42,960
This is a celebration ceremony

77
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:44,120
I carefully prepared for you.

78
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,200
Humor me.

79
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:45,880
Come.

80
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:58,760
I'm actually quite curious.

81
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:00,800
Tell me,

82
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:04,720
what's it like to kill the one you love with your own hands?

83
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,840
How does it feel?

84
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:09,400
The person I should kill the most

85
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,280
is you.

86
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:17,640
Do you think you still have a chance?

87
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:20,170
You've already destroyed the Yao family.

88
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:21,760
Your father's murderer,

89
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:23,360
you killed him too.

90
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,960
Why not just be Yao Shengsheng

91
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:31,400
and be the wife of Song Huainan?

92
00:08:31,840 --> 00:08:33,480
I can make it up to you.

93
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,580
Make it up to me?

94
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,039
With what?

95
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:40,240
You killed so many people.

96
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:41,559
Song Huainan,

97
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,600
you'll die a horrible death.

98
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:51,800
Fine.

99
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:53,580
It doesn't matter.

100
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:55,240
We have plenty of time.

101
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,240
In the coming days,

102
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,800
you can think it over.

103
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:58,560
Maybe

104
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:01,560
you'll change your mind, right?

105
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,000
Guards!

106
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,480
Yes, sir.

107
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,880
Take the Young Mistress

108
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,160
away.

109
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,200
Yes, Marshal.

110
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:14,080
It's just a shame about the steak.

111
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:42,880
If you use a knife,

112
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,960
the abdomen isn't protected by ribs,

113
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,420
so one strike can be fatal.

114
00:09:46,880 --> 00:09:49,080
But as long as vital organs are avoided,

115
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,960
the wound won't be fatal.

116
00:09:59,200 --> 00:09:59,560
Tang Mengjia

